<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Gelan Eagles - U13 & U15 Soccer Club</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-gray-100">
    <header class="bg-green-600 text-white">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-6">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center">
                <div class="flex items-center mb-4 md:mb-0">
                    <i class="fas fa-futbol text-4xl mr-4"></i>
                    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">Gelan Eagles</h1>
                </div>
                <nav>
                    <ul class="flex flex-wrap justify-center space-x-4">
                        <li><a href="/" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/about" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300">About</a></li>
                        <li><a href="/teams" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300">Teams</a></li>
 <li><a href="/blog" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300">Blog</a></li>
 <li><a href="/shop" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300">Shop</a></li>

                        <li><a href="/contact" class="hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300">Contact</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </nav>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section class="bg-green-500 text-white py-20">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Gelan Eagles</h2>
                <p class="text-xl mb-8">Nurturing young talent and fostering a love for soccer since 2010</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h3>
                        <p class="mb-4">At Gelan Eagles, our mission is to provide a nurturing environment for young soccer players to develop their skills, build character, and foster a lifelong love for the beautiful game. We believe in the power of sports to shape young minds and bodies, creating well-rounded individuals both on and off the field.</p>
                        <p>Through our U13 and U15 programs, we aim to:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4">
                            <li>Develop technical soccer skills</li>
                            <li>Promote teamwork and sportsmanship</li>
                            <li>Build confidence and leadership abilities</li>
                            <li>Encourage a healthy, active lifestyle</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="order-first md:order-last mb-8 md:mb-0">
                        <img src="u15.jpg" alt="Gelan Eagles Team" class="rounded-lg shadow-md w-full h-auto">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-green-100 py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Our Values</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-handshake text-4xl text-green-600 mb-4"></i>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Respect</h4>
                        <p>We teach our players to respect themselves, their teammates, opponents, and officials.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-users text-4xl text-green-600 mb-4"></i>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Teamwork</h4>
                        <p>We emphasize the importance of working together to achieve common goals.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-trophy text-4xl text-green-600 mb-4"></i>
                        <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Excellence</h4>
                        <p>We encourage our players to strive for excellence in all aspects of their lives.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">Our Coaches</h3>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md overflow-hidden">
                        <img src="/coach.jpg" alt="Coach Yohannes Legesse" class="w-full h-48 object-cover">
                        <div class="p-6">
                            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Yohannes Legesse</h4>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Head Coach, U15 Team</p>
                            <p>Coach Yohannes has over 8 years of experience in youth soccer development.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-green-500 text-white py-16">
            <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Join the Gelan Eagles Family</h3>
                <p class="text-xl mb-8">Be part of a supportive community that's passionate about soccer and youth development.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="bg-yellow-400 text-green-800 font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-full hover:bg-yellow-300 transition duration-300">Contact Us</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="bg-green-800 text-white py-8">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <p>&copy; 2023 Gelan Eagles Soccer Club. All rights reserved.</p>
            <div class="mt-4">
                <a href="#" class="text-2xl mx-2 hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300"><i class="fab fa-facebook"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="text-2xl mx-2 hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
                <a href="#" class="text-2xl mx-2 hover:text-yellow-300 transition duration-300"><i class="fab fa-instagram"></i></a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
